## 
leetcode<https://leetcode-cn.com/problems/bulls-and-cows>

>  Bulls and Cows  
>   
> +  "Bulls", 
> +  "Cows", 
>   
> secret guess   
>  "xAyB" x  y A B  
>  

### 
#### 
` secret `` guess `` secret[i]=guess[i] `

` guess[i]  secret[i] `` secret `` guess `` 10 `09` secret `` guess `

##### 
+ ` O(N) `` N ` ` secret ` 

+ ` O(C) `` C=10 `  

### 
#### Python
```python
# 
class Solution:
    def getHint(self, secret: str, guess: str) -> str:
        bulls = 0
        secretCount, guessCount = [0] * 10, [0] * 10
        for s, g in zip(secret, guess):
            if s == g:
                bulls += 1
            else:
                secretCount[int(s)] += 1
                guessCount[int(g)] += 1
        cows = sum(min(s, g) for s, g in zip(secretCount, guessCount))
        return f'{bulls}A{cows}B'
```
